data.description: Back on the market due to buyer's contingent home not selling. Welcome to this inviting 3-bedroom, 1-bath home nestled in the heart of Estes Park. Recent updates have given this residence a fresh and modern feel, while still embracing the area's rustic charm. The interior features Luxury Vinyl Plank flooring for both a stylish look and easy maintenance. A new metal roof adds durability and fits in perfectly with the mountain surroundings. Step out onto the expansive deck that runs along both the front and side yard, and take in the stunning views of Lumpy Ridge - a truly picturesque backdrop. The bathroom has been remodeled to encompass heated tile flooring and a new vanity with double sinks. Solid alder wood interior doors add a touch of elegance throughout the home. The kitchen has been updated with new appliances, combining both function and style. Whether you're cooking for your family or entertaining guests, this space is designed to accommodate your needs. This a great opportunity to own a piece of Estes Park where modern updates and natural beauty come together in perfect harmony. This home offers both comfort and the opportunity to enjoy the serene mountain lifestyle.
